Fans of the world's greatest paranormal detective can find two of the best Hellboy stories to date in this set of short stories from Hellboy: The Troll Witch and Others and The Dark Horse Book of Hauntings, featuring work by comics legends P. Craig Russell and Mike Mignola.

The Vampire of Prague. If you play cards with the dead you get cursed and roam the streets untill you're faced with Hellboy.

Dr. Carp's Experiment. Hellboy visits a haunted house in Long Island (NY).

description:
If Nick Barrow can stay alive for 21 days he'll die happy. Everyone Nick knows wants him dead; Mob bosses, contract killers, and dirty cops. Performing the last act of a desperate man, Nick takes out a million dollar insurance policy on himself, payable to his estranged daughter. The problem? The policy doesn't take effect for 21 days. Nick knows they'll be lucky to be alive for twenty-one hours.

You give a tip for a lucrative heist to the Russian mob but then four of them die including the son of the boss. If he could just stay alive for only 21 days and protect his estranged daughter he would accept his fate.. death.
name: OGN
